---
title: Sri Lankan Potato, Cauliflower & Chicken Dhal with Garlic Tortilla Dippers
description: Put that take-away flyer down because we've got something in store for you. Sri Lankan spices work their magic with
hearty lentils, chicken and creamy coconut milk in our new favourite dhal recipe. Oven-baked tortilla chips work a treat for
scooping up the deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65d5afa452b7e6609bab1b39-4298938f.jpeg
